title: Thom Hartmann Program - September 03 2013
description:
September 03, 2013
The Thom Hartmann Program 


Hour One: Thom's thoughts on Syria. Rules of War... / Plus, Rep. Grayson says "Tell Congress: Don't Attack Syria" - Congressman Alan Grayson (D-FL, 9th District)


Hour Two: Hey McDonalds...time to supersize those wages!  Leo Gerard, United Steeworkers on the current state of the labor movement in the U.S.


Hour Three: Rules of War, part 2. Plus Your thoughts on Syria, and Obama's plan to ask Congress for approval
